<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَالجِمَاعُ قَبْلَ التَّحَلُّلِ الأَوَّلِ فِي حَجٍّ،<span class="c5"> وَقَبْلَ فَرَاغِ سَعْيٍ فِي عُمْرَةٍ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> مُفْسِدٌ لِنُسُكِهِمَا مُطْلَقاً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَفِيهِ لِحَجٍّ: بَدَنَةٌ،<span class="c5"> وَلِعُمْرَةٍ:</span> شَاةٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَيَمْضِيَانِ فِي فَاسِدِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَيَقْضِيَانِهِ مُطْلَقاً إِنْ كَانَا مُكَلَّفَيْنِ فَوْراً.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَإِلَّا بَعْدَ التَّكْلِيفِ وَفِعْلِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> حَجَّةِ الإِسْلَامِ فَوْراً.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا يَفْسُدُ النُّسُكُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> بِمُبَاشَرَةٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَجِبُ بِهَا:</span> بَدَنَةٌ إِنْ أَنْزَلَ، وَإِلَّا شَاةٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَلَا بِوَطْءٍ فِي حَجٍّ بَعْدَ التَّحَلُّلِ الأَوَّلِ وَقَبْلَ الثَّانِي.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- لَكِنْ يَفْسُدُ الإِحْرَامُ، فَيُحْرِمُ مِنَ الحِلِّ لِيَطُوفَ للزِّيَارَةِ فِي إِحْرَامٍ صَحِيحٍ، وَيَسْعَى إِنْ لَمْ يَكُنْ سَعَى.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَعَلَيْهِ شَاةٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَإِحْرَامُ امْرَأَةٍ كَرَجُلٍ،<span class="c5"> إِلَّا فِي:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> لُبْسِ مَخِيطٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (فعل) سقطت من (أ) و (ج) و (د).</p> </div>